                     <interp inst="t18120219-16-off93" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18120219-16-cd94" type="crimeDate">20th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120219-16-off93 t18120219-16-cd94"></join>, a shawl, value 1 s. two handkerchiefs, value 1 s. four shirts, value 16 s. three half shirts, value 3 s. and two collars, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120219-16-victim186" type="victimName">
